      <body>
         <hcontainer name="regulation" eId="regulation-1">
            <heading>Citation and commencement</heading>
            <num>1.</num>
            <content>
               <p>These Regulations may be cited as the Non-Domestic Rates (Relief for New and Improved Properties) (Scotland) Amendment Regulations 2019 and come into force on 31 March 2019.</p>
            </content>
         </hcontainer>
         <hcontainer name="regulation" eId="regulation-2">
            <heading>Amendment of the Non-Domestic Rates (Relief for New and Improved Properties) (Scotland) Regulations 2019</heading>
            <num>2.</num>
            <paragraph eId="regulation-2-1">
               <num>(1)</num>
               <content>
                  <p>The Non-Domestic Rates (Relief for New and Improved Properties) (Scotland) Regulations 2019<noteRef href="#f00002" class="footnote" marker="2"/> are amended as follows.</p>
               </content>
            </paragraph>
            <paragraph eId="regulation-2-2">
               <num>(2)</num>
               <content>
                  <p>For the formula in regulation 10(5)(b) substitute the formula—<mod>
                        <quotedStructure startQuote="“" endQuote="”" ukl:TargetClass="unknown" ukl:TargetSubClass="unknown" ukl:Context="unknown">
                           <p>
                              <subFlow name="inlineMathWrapper">
                                 <foreign>
                                    <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline" altimg="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ssi/2019/116/images/ssi_20190116_en_001">
                                       <semantics>
                                          <mrow>
                                             <mfrac>
                                                <mrow>
                                                   <mi>B</mi>
                                                   <mi>L</mi>
                                                   <mo>×</mo>
                                                   <mn>1.527</mn>
                                                   <mo>×</mo>
                                                   <mi>A</mi>
                                                   <mi>R</mi>
                                                   <mi>V</mi>
                                                </mrow>
                                                <mrow>
                                                   <mn>366</mn>
                                                   <mo>×</mo>
                                                   <mi>R</mi>
                                                   <mi>V</mi>
                                                </mrow>
                                             </mfrac>
                                          </mrow>
                                          <annotation encoding="MathType-MTEF"/>
                                       </semantics>
                                    </math>
                                 </foreign>
                              </subFlow>
                           </p>
                        </quotedStructure>
                     </mod>
                     <inline name="AppendText">.</inline>
                  </p>
               </content>
            </paragraph>
         </hcontainer>
